Class CafeteriaMapper

java.lang.Object
com.cafe.backend.entity.mapper.CafeteriaMapper
public class CafeteriaMapper extends Object
CafeteriaMapper is a utility class used for mapping between CafeteriaEntity and CafeteriaDTO. This class contains methods to convert a CafeteriaEntity to a CafeteriaDTO and vice versa. It is designed to handle the transformation between entity and DTO representations for the cafeteria data.

The methods in this class will throw a DataMappingException if the input is null.
